Take a heading...

702
01:18:52,974 --> 01:18:54,453
Not that shit! Point!

703
01:18:54,494 --> 01:18:55,609
There.

704
01:18:55,654 --> 01:18:57,963
All right, I got it.

705
01:19:15,174 --> 01:19:18,405
Mr Christian! Mr Christian!

706
01:19:18,454 --> 01:19:22,447
Pump up this boat! And shave off
that dreadful moustache.

707
01:19:22,494 --> 01:19:26,931
England expects every man
to do his duty. Fire when ready!

708
01:19:27,014 --> 01:19:30,006
Damn the torpedoes!
Full speed ahead!

709
01:19:30,054 --> 01:19:33,205
This will be our finest hour.

710
01:19:35,494 --> 01:19:37,086
Oh, shit.

711
01:19:37,214 --> 01:19:39,887
Hey, Bligh, someone pop your balloon?

712
01:19:39,934 --> 01:19:42,368
No problem, no problem.

713
01:20:12,294 --> 01:20:14,046
Balance the boat!

714
01:20:28,254 --> 01:20:30,290
Watch out!

715
01:20:33,054 --> 01:20:34,726
Do something!

716
01:20:40,574 --> 01:20:42,007
Timmy! Brooke!

717
01:20:42,094 --> 01:20:43,652
Hey! Look out.

718
01:20:48,254 --> 01:20:50,006
Where is it?

719
01:20:50,054 --> 01:20:53,171
- Get me out of here!
- I'll get you out.

720
01:20:53,214 --> 01:20:54,363
Larry!

721
01:20:54,414 --> 01:20:56,689
Larry! Turn!

722
01:20:57,134 --> 01:20:58,965
Turn!

723
01:21:04,214 --> 01:21:05,966
It's OK.

724
01:21:09,014 --> 01:21:12,290
- Hurry up!
- Mike's out there.

725
01:21:12,334 --> 01:21:14,006
Out of the water.

726
01:21:18,214 --> 01:21:21,126
Somebody look out for Mike!

727
01:21:22,334 --> 01:21:23,733
Hang on to something!

728
01:21:23,774 --> 01:21:26,163
Mike, get out of there!

729
01:21:27,254 --> 01:21:29,085
Hold on!

730
01:21:33,014 --> 01:21:34,527
Oh, my God.

731
01:21:34,574 --> 01:21:36,326
Mike!

732
01:21:37,374 --> 01:21:39,365
Brody!

733
01:21:39,414 --> 01:21:40,688
