Amity Launch to Air Patrol One.

758
01:24:17,774 --> 01:24:19,969
Amity Launch to Air Patrol One.

759
01:24:20,014 --> 01:24:21,606
Do you read me?

760
01:24:21,654 --> 01:24:24,168
'This is Air Patrol.
That you, Brody?'

761
01:24:24,214 --> 01:24:27,126
Yeah. Do you have
a fix on those kids?

762
01:24:27,174 --> 01:24:28,926
'Negative. I'm still down. '

763
01:24:28,974 --> 01:24:32,284
Get the hell up
because I'm out here alone.

764
01:24:32,334 --> 01:24:34,484
'Brody, I got to switch frequencies.

765
01:24:34,534 --> 01:24:37,924
'Call my boss.
I'll meet you by Francis Shoal. Out. '

766
01:24:39,974 --> 01:24:42,932
Francis Shoal?
Where the hell is Francis Shoal?

767
01:24:56,054 --> 01:24:58,010
Shit.

768
01:24:58,054 --> 01:25:00,204
I'm all alone out here.

769
01:25:40,014 --> 01:25:41,891
Anyone want to play charades?

770
01:25:44,094 --> 01:25:45,083
No.

771
01:25:46,174 --> 01:25:49,246
All we have to do is land
at Cable Junction and wait.

772
01:25:49,294 --> 01:25:51,683
How will we do that on this garbage?

773
01:25:54,614 --> 01:25:56,764
What's after Cable Junction?

774
01:25:56,814 --> 01:25:59,806
The Atlantic. Then Ireland.

775
01:26:03,494 --> 01:26:05,769
God, I'm hungry.

776
01:26:34,734 --> 01:26:36,611
Air Patrol to Base.

777
01:26:36,654 --> 01:26:40,329
I have a positive location
on that sailing party.

778
01:26:40,374 --> 01:26:42,524
Disabled and adrift,

779
01:26:42,574 --> 01:26:46,044
about three quarters of a mile west
of Cable Junction,

780
01:26:46,094 --> 01:26:48,688
wind and tide carrying them due east.

781
01:27:35,014 --> 01:27:37,084
Is everyone OK? Is anybody hurt?

782
01:27:37,134 --> 01:27:38,203
No!

783
01:27:38,254 --> 01:27:40,529
I'll tow you to Cable Junction,

784
01:27:40,574 --> 01:27:43,168
then call the Coast Guard.

785
01:27:45,054 --> 01:27:46,965
Throw me a line.

786
01:27:47,014 --> 01:27:49,369
Take it easy. Here we go.

787
01:27:49,414 --> 01:27:51,882
- Oh, what a day
- Here you go!

788
01:28:01,334 --> 01:28:02,687
OK.

789
01:28:04,734 --> 01:28:07,248
- Now, hold on to something.
- OK.

790
01:28:07,294 --> 01:28:09,569
- Hurry up!
- Better hang on.

791
01:30:05,334 --> 01:30:06,847
Sean.

792
01:30:06,894 --> 01:30:09,613
- Sean!
- Sean!

793
01:30:11,214 --> 01:30:12,932
Sean!

794
01:30:13,894 --> 01:30:15,327
Sean!

795
01:30:16,494 --> 01:30:17,813
Get him in the boat.

796
01:30:19,334 --> 01:30:20,847
- Sean!
- Come on!

797
01:30:20,894 --> 01:30:22,213
Get aboard.

798
01:30:22,254 --> 01:30:24,165
- Hurry!
- Come on.

799
01:30:27,214 --> 01:30:28,852
Come on.

800
01:30:33,774 --> 01:30:35,651
I can't get up.

801
01:30:39,854 --> 01:30:41,412
No!

802
01:30:45,174 --> 01:30:46,163
No!

803
01:30:50,214 --> 01:30:53,286
Take her to the hospital
and meet me at the office.

804
01:30:57,174 --> 01:30:59,529
Try to understand my position...

805
01:30:59,574 --> 01:31:01,804
Tina will be all right. Are you OK?

806
01:31:03,294 --> 01:31:06,013
Ellen, I'm sorry.
Believe me, I'm sorry.

807
01:31:06,054 --> 01:31:07,726
I was only thinking of...

808
01:31:07,774 --> 01:31:09,924
I don't give a damn what you think.

809
01:31:09,974 --> 01:31:13,762
A boy is dead and my son and husband
are still out there.

810
01:31:59,054 --> 01:32:01,773
Amity Launch to Harbour Patrol.

811
01:32:08,254 --> 01:32:10,085
Amity Launch to Harbour...

812
01:32:11,654 --> 01:32:13,053
Damn it!

813
01:32:19,934 --> 01:32:22,323
Sean, catch the rope!

814
01:32:22,374 --> 01:32:25,366
- Come on, the rope!
- Sean!

815
01:32:25,414 --> 01:32:27,006
Sean, catch the rope!

816
01:32:27,054 --> 01:32:28,772
Sean, the rope!

817
01:32:28,814 --> 01:32:32,489
- Come on, Sean!
- Come on, Sean!

818
01:32:32,534 --> 01:32:34,013
Come on!

819
01:32:34,054 --> 01:32:35,123
Sean!

820
01:32:35,174 --> 01:32:37,085
Sean, catch the rope!

821
01:32:37,134 --> 01:32:38,692
The rope, Sean!

822
01:32:38,734 --> 01:32:40,372
Come on, Sean!

823
01:32:40,414 --> 01:32:43,053
Come on!
You've gotta help or it won't work.

824
01:32:43,094 --> 01:32:44,732
Will you stop?

825
01:32:44,774 --> 01:32:47,208
Come on, Sean, wake up!

826
01:32:47,774 --> 01:32:49,366
Pick it up!

827
01:32:51,054 --> 01:32:52,373
Sean!

828
01:32:53,334 --> 01:32:55,052
Sean, goddamn it.

829
01:32:55,094 --> 01:32:58,131
Sean, listen to me
or I'll break your ass!

830
01:33:02,334 --> 01:33:03,562
OK, come on.

831
01:33:05,014 --> 01:33:07,130
OK, Sean, now listen.

832
01:33:07,174 --> 01:33:10,371
We'll throw you this rope
and you better catch it.

833
01:33:10,414 --> 01:33:12,052
Sean, you ready?

834
01:33:12,094 --> 01:33:14,050
Here it comes, kid.

835
01:33:18,294 --> 01:33:20,012
Get it, Sean.

836
01:33:20,054 --> 01:33:22,204
Sean, get it.

837
01:33:22,254 --> 01:33:24,449
Come on, get it.

838
01:33:24,494 --> 01:33:27,930
Good. Now tie it around
the centreboard.

839
01:33:27,974 --> 01:33:29,771
Tie it tight.

840
01:33:32,254 --> 01:33:33,767
You ready? Hang on.

841
01:33:33,814 --> 01:33:35,088
Hold on.

842
01:33:35,134 --> 01:33:36,806
Hang on, OK?

843
01:33:36,854 --> 01:33:38,890
Here we go. Hold on tight.

844
01:33:49,054 --> 01:33:50,533
OK, kid.

845
01:33:52,094 --> 01:33:54,050
Take it easy.

846
01:33:56,174 --> 01:33:57,732
Come on.

847
01:33:57,774 --> 01:33:59,173
OK.

848
01:34:02,774 --> 01:34:05,242
- Get him out!
- Come on.

849
01:34:15,054 --> 01:34:17,204
Oh, God. Are you OK, kid?

850
01:34:17,254 --> 01:34:19,370
I thought we lost you.

851
01:34:26,414 --> 01:34:28,245
Cable Junction's ahead.

852
01:34:29,014 --> 01:34:31,289
- Can we make it?
- I don't know.

853
01:34:31,334 --> 01:34:33,643
- Hey, I was just asking!
- I know.

854
01:34:36,614 --> 01:34:38,206
How's she doing?

855
01:34:38,254 --> 01:34:40,165
Just got to keep her warm.

856
01:34:43,334 --> 01:34:45,768
Somebody help me
and we could steer this.

857
01:34:47,134 --> 01:34:49,443
What are you playing
with a tube for?

858
01:34:49,494 --> 01:34:51,405
- If everyone...
- Shut up!

859
01:34:51,454 --> 01:34:54,412
I'm sorry
but I can't stop thinking about this!

860
01:34:54,454 --> 01:34:55,967
Well, you better try!

861
01:34:56,014 --> 01:34:58,767
Oh, God, please help.

862
01:34:59,894 --> 01:35:01,612
Jesus...

863
01:35:01,654 --> 01:35:03,406
Holy Mary,

864
01:35:03,454 --> 01:35:05,331
Mother of Christ,

865
01:35:05,374 --> 01:35:07,046
please help us.

866
01:35:08,974 --> 01:35:10,885
Please help us.

867
01:35:12,054 --> 01:35:13,726
We're begging.

868
01:35:17,374 --> 01:35:19,490
Please save us.

869
01:36:19,494 --> 01:36:21,450
Oh, thank Christ.

870
01:36:29,534 --> 01:36:31,729
Here, take that back to the cleat.

871
01:36:35,934 --> 01:36:38,164
- What happened?
- I'm OK.

872
01:36:38,214 --> 01:36:40,728
- Sure?
- A shark hit us.

873
01:36:40,774 --> 01:36:42,651
Sean's out there.

874
01:36:42,694 --> 01:36:46,084
- What?
- He wanted to come.

875
01:36:46,134 --> 01:36:47,408
Where are they?

876
01:36:47,454 --> 01:36:51,049
They're in the current
heading for Cable Junction.

877
01:36:51,094 --> 01:36:54,564
All right, get to the lighthouse
and stay there, OK?

878
01:36:54,614 --> 01:36:57,208
- Stay there.
- I'm sorry, Dad.

879
01:36:57,254 --> 01:36:59,893
Forget it.
Just get to the lighthouse.

880
01:37:09,174 --> 01:37:11,688
- We're almost there.
- It's not gonna work.

881
01:37:11,734 --> 01:37:13,770
Come on, more to port.

882
01:37:13,814 --> 01:37:15,884
Keep it going. We'll make it.

883
01:37:16,734 --> 01:37:18,645
More to port, goddamn it!

884
01:37:18,694 --> 01:37:20,525
All the way over.

885
01:37:21,494 --> 01:37:25,089
Larry, are we going to make it
to the island?

886
01:37:25,134 --> 01:37:27,364
We're steering for it, kid.

887
01:37:28,294 --> 01:37:30,205
But the wind drift is lateral.

888
01:37:30,254 --> 01:37:31,687
What does that mean?

889
01:37:31,734 --> 01:37:35,044
It means that we're going sideways.
We're going that way.

890
01:37:35,094 --> 01:37:37,608
- We were heading right for it.
- Not now.

891
01:37:37,654 --> 01:37:40,612
Shit. Shit, shit, shit.

892
01:37:51,494 --> 01:37:53,485
Wait! Stop paddling.

893
01:37:53,534 --> 01:37:56,446
- What about the island?
- The shark!

894
01:38:20,774 --> 01:38:23,652
- What's happening?
- I think we're stuck.

895
01:38:23,694 --> 01:38:25,685
It's just the bottom.

896
01:38:25,734 --> 01:38:28,328
- It's that thing.
- It's just the bottom.

897
01:38:28,374 --> 01:38:33,164
No, it's not the bottom.
It's that thing! It's gonna kill us!

898
01:38:33,214 --> 01:38:34,613
Jackie, shut up!

899
01:38:34,654 --> 01:38:38,533
- No! It's going to kill us!
- Shut up! Shut up!

900
01:38:38,574 --> 01:38:40,212
Leave her alone!

901
01:38:40,254 --> 01:38:42,165
Then you take care of her.

902
01:38:42,214 --> 01:38:45,092
- She's hysterical, beating...
- Sit down.

903
01:38:45,134 --> 01:38:46,647
Be quiet!

904
01:38:47,894 --> 01:38:49,373
Shut up!

905
01:38:49,414 --> 01:38:50,847
Listen!

906
01:38:50,894 --> 01:38:53,328
- She shouldn't freak out.
- Listen!

907
01:38:55,414 --> 01:38:57,211
You hear it?

908
01:39:09,774 --> 01:39:12,493
Over there! It's coming towards us.

909
01:39:15,814 --> 01:39:17,167
It's Dad! Dad!

910
01:39:24,574 --> 01:39:25,973
Dad!

911
01:39:43,454 --> 01:39:47,447
Oh, cool. Cool, come on...

912
01:40:04,694 --> 01:40:06,764
Pull yourselves over
and we'll get out of here.

913
01:40:06,814 --> 01:40:10,409
We can't.
We're stuck on the bottom here.

914
01:40:10,454 --> 01:40:12,206
I'll get you closer.
We'll come aboard.

915
01:40:12,254 --> 01:40:15,166
- Pull us alongside.
- Please hurry!

916
01:40:15,214 --> 01:40:17,091
All right, hold it steady.

917
01:40:18,614 --> 01:40:19,967
Oh, sh...!

918
01:40:31,014 --> 01:40:32,003
Wait!

919
01:40:38,094 --> 01:40:39,413
Dad!

920
01:40:50,614 --> 01:40:52,650
I'm all right. Hold on.

921
01:41:01,334 --> 01:41:04,167
All right,
take this and I'll get you over.

922
01:41:10,454 --> 01:41:12,410
- All right, tie it on.
- OK.

923
01:41:22,734 --> 01:41:25,965
All right,
pull these hooks over with the rope.

924
01:41:26,014 --> 01:41:30,132
Secure them to the raft then I'll
pull you back with the winch, OK?

925
01:41:30,174 --> 01:41:31,607
OK.

926
01:41:57,014 --> 01:41:58,811
All right, pull it over.

927
01:42:11,574 --> 01:42:12,973
It's stuck.

928
01:42:13,014 --> 01:42:16,609
Wait a minute, I'll put...
I'll put it in reverse.

929
01:42:59,014 --> 01:43:00,333
Lucy!

930
01:43:00,374 --> 01:43:03,366
Lucy, look out!

931
01:43:03,414 --> 01:43:06,326
Oh, my God! No! No!

932
01:43:09,494 --> 01:43:11,086
Lucy!

933
01:43:19,614 --> 01:43:21,445
No!

934
01:43:22,254 --> 01:43:24,722
Oh, my God! No!

935
01:43:24,774 --> 01:43:25,923
Dad!

936
01:43:27,774 --> 01:43:29,287
Hold on!

937
01:43:57,734 --> 01:43:59,326
Dad!

938
01:44:06,574 --> 01:44:07,893
Get away!

939
01:44:07,934 --> 01:44:09,413
No!

940
01:44:12,894 --> 01:44:14,532
Get away!

941
01:44:28,054 --> 01:44:29,407
No!

942
01:44:35,934 --> 01:44:36,923
Sean!

943
01:45:35,494 --> 01:45:38,406
- Where'd he go?
- Where is he?

944
01:45:59,014 --> 01:46:01,403
- There he is!
- Over there.

945
01:46:13,974 --> 01:46:16,044
What the hell are you doing?

946
01:46:20,454 --> 01:46:22,172
Get out of there!

947
01:46:24,214 --> 01:46:26,364
He's heading right for you!

948
01:46:30,854 --> 01:46:33,414
All right, you big bastard, come on.

949
01:46:34,094 --> 01:46:35,925
I got something for you now.

950
01:46:38,414 --> 01:46:42,168
That's it! That a boy! Come on!

951
01:46:42,214 --> 01:46:43,567
Right over here!

952
01:46:43,614 --> 01:46:45,172
Dad!

953
01:46:45,214 --> 01:46:47,250
That's it. Come on.

954
01:46:47,294 --> 01:46:50,923
No! Get out of the way!

955
01:46:52,054 --> 01:46:53,203
Don't do it!

956
01:46:54,574 --> 01:46:56,883
Get away! Get away!

957
01:46:56,934 --> 01:46:58,765
Dad! Watch out!

958
01:46:58,814 --> 01:46:59,803
Come on!

959
01:46:59,854 --> 01:47:01,685
Look out!

960
01:47:01,734 --> 01:47:03,133
Open wide!

961
01:47:03,174 --> 01:47:05,608
Open wide, say "ah"!

962
01:47:35,614 --> 01:47:37,605
He did it. He got it!

963
01:48:02,254 --> 01:48:05,644
He did it! He did it! He did it!

964
01:48:05,694 --> 01:48:08,208
Did he get it? It's dead?

965
01:48:08,254 --> 01:48:10,245
It's dead!

966
01:48:19,454 --> 01:48:21,285
Oh, thank you.

967
01:48:21,334 --> 01:48:24,053
Thank you,
thank you, thank you...

968
01:48:38,054 --> 01:48:41,012
- And you...
- They made me go with them.

969
01:48:45,974 --> 01:48:47,168
Sure they did!
